summary: This cable details the planned departure of TEJANA from Key West on February 25th, 1961, for Operation JEAN, carrying cargo and four trainees: Emilio Martinez alias Ernesto Guerra Vidal, Oliverio Toneu alias Antonio Del Monte Caballero, Rafael Alvarez Fernandez-Garrido alias Maximo Alonso Bermudez, and Carlos Poveda alias Calixto Bergnes Braudet.
title: Cable regarding TEJANA departure for Operation JEAN
